### Order Service HTTP Requests

@host = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{host}}/actuator/health

### Metrics
GET {{host}}/actuator/metrics

### Create new order
POST {{host}}/api/v1/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "123",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "456",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Get order by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/order/123
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all orders
GET {{host}}/api/v1/order
Content-Type: application/json
